EncounterIntro: The adventuring duo find a fruit tree with numerous rare fruit hanging from its upper branches
PlayerAction: Emma tries to shake the tree with all her might.
RewardFeedback: Emma's efforts make several of the fruit fall. She will be able to sell these back in the village.
PunishFeedback: Emma does not manage to shake any of the fruit loose. She hurts her shoulder in the process.

EncounterIntro: As the duo enter a forest they stumble upon a heavily worn wooden board that reads “forest map”.
PlayerAction: Yuxi relies on her intelligence to parse the details of the map.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi successfully deciphers the map. She finds a path that avoids nearby hazards.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi gets confused by the worn map. She leads the duo into a quicksand pit causing them to drop some valubles.

EncounterIntro: The duo stumbles upon a elvish merchant. The merchant says "solve my riddle to earn a prize or else pay me a token!"
PlayerAction: Emma relies on her wit to make sense of the riddle.
RewardFeedback: Emma solves the riddle. She is rewarded with a small silver trinket.
PunishFeedback: Emma is unable to make sense of the riddle. She is obligated to pay the merchant.

EncounterIntro: A fissue connects the two sides of a valley.
PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to use her athleticism to jump across the fissure.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi successfully jumps the gap. She is able to secure a rope to throw back across.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi barely grabs on to the edge. She is able to climb up and secure a rope but is injured in the process.

EncounterIntro: An ancient statue stands before the adventurers. On it is etched an unfamiliar language.
PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to rely on her intelligence to decipher the language.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi is able to  decipher a set of instructions to a nearby cache. She is led to a cache of small gemstones.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi is unable to make sense of the language. She is left empty handed.

EncounterIntro: The duo enters a clearing where a formidable troll awaits. A sign nearby states, Defeat the troll to proceed.""
PlayerAction: Emma charges forward. She swings her weapon with all her might.
RewardFeedback: Emma parries the troll's counterattack and makes a critical hit. She defeats the troll with minimal injuries.
PunishFeedback: The troll proves resistant against Emma’s attack and counters their attack. She suffers damage from several attacks before felling the troll.

EncounterIntro: As the duo continues they notice a shiny metal embedded in a nearby rock face.
PlayerAction: Yuxi picks up a nearby rock. She uses the rock to try to smash away some of the metal.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi is successful. She stores some of the ore to prospect later.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi accidentally bashes their hand in the process. She suffers an injury.

EncounterIntro: The duo stumbles across the camp of a known murdering bandit.
PlayerAction: Emma tries to think of a clever way to subdue the bandit. She hides while pondering.
RewardFeedback: Emma navigates a path behind the bandit. She hits them over the head with rock.
PunishFeedback: Emma attempts to sneak behind the bandit. She is caught and is painfully struck before subduing the bandit.

EncounterIntro: The duo arrives a large rock tall enough to give a better view of the area.
PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to muscle her way up the rock.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi successfully climbs to the top of the rock. She spots a shortcut to a known hunting ground.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi was unable to clumb the rock. She falls on her shoulder and suffers an injury.

EncounterIntro: In the bandit camp, the players are presented with a locked ornate chest.
PlayerAction: Emma relies on her wit to try to decipher the combination on the lock.
RewardFeedback: Emma unlocks the chest revealing a pouch of gold inside. She puts the treasure in her pack for safekeeping.
PunishFeedback: Emma triggers a trap and an arrow is launched at them. She suffers damage.

EncounterIntro: As the duo continue they stumble across a rabid dog. The dog begins chargins.
PlayerAction: Emma attempts to overpower the charging dog using her pack to absorb the bite.
RewardFeedback: Emma successfully overpowers the dog. She redirects the dog and shoves it down an steep adjacent hill.
PunishFeedback: Emma is able to absorb the brunt of the attack and pushes the dog down an adjacent hill. She gets several scratches in the process.

EncounterIntro: As the duo continue their path is blocked by a dense and thorny mass of bushes.
PlayerAction: Yuxi attempts to slash at the branches with all her might.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi successfully cuts through the branches. She suffers no ill effects.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi is able to cut through after considerable effort. She suffers some injuries in the process.

EncounterIntro: The duo come across a tree strump with glowing mushrooms growing on top.
PlayerAction: Yuxi tries to rely on her intelligence to decipher the species of mushroom.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi recalls that these mushrooms have healing properties. She stores them in their pack to sell later.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi misremembers the mushroom's species. She is zapped by the mushroom's glow when they try to pick them.

EncounterIntro: The duo come across a set of track leading off the path
PlayerAction: Emma attempts to be clever. She looks for clues to parse the direction of the tracks.
RewardFeedback: Emma identies the direction of the tracks. She successfully avoids stepping on a nearby python in the process.
PunishFeedback: Emma identies the direction of the tracks. She accidentally steps on a python and is bitten suffering an injury in the process.

EncounterIntro: A boar emerges from the nearby foliage.
PlayerAction: Yuxi attempts to strike the boar with all her strength.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi successfully strikes down the boar. She is able to reclaim some meat to sell later.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi wasn't strong enough to strike down the boar. She is tripped by the boar as it escapes suffering an injury in the process.

EncounterIntro: The duo come across a wagon stuck in the mud and a distressed villager.
PlayerAction: Emma attempts to rely on her intelligence to find a solution.
RewardFeedback: Emma was able to find a strong branch to lever the wagon out of the mud. She was rewarded with some gold coins.
PunishFeedback: Emma was unable to think of a solution. She is thanked by the upset villager for trying….

EncounterIntro: The duo come across a forest gnome requesting aid to rescue their pet racoon from a tree.
PlayerAction: Emma attempts to use her strength and athleticism to climb the tree.
RewardFeedback: Emma was able to climb the tree and rescue the racoon.  She is rewarded with a few gemstones.
PunishFeedback: Emma was unable to climb the tree and scares the racoon in the process. The gnome turns some of her valubles into rocks.

EncounterIntro: The duo come across two traveling mercenaries engaged in a heated argument about directions.
PlayerAction: Yuxi attempts to rely on her intelligence to decipher directions for the mercenaries.
RewardFeedback: Yuxi was able to successfully direct the travelers. She is rewarded with some gold coins.
PunishFeedback: Yuxi was unable to help and is punched for wasting the mercenary's time. She is bruised in the process.
